import React, { Fragment, Component } from 'react'

import { Categories } from '../../utils/Mocks/Categories'

import '../../../src/App.css'

import {
  StyledContainer,
  CardContainer,
  CardDiv,
  CardImg,
  CardTitle,
  CardDescription
} from './styled'

export default class CategoryCards extends Component {
  render() {
    console.log(Categories)
    return (
      <StyledContainer>
        <CardContainer>
          <CardDiv>
            {Categories.map(category => (
              <Fragment>
                <CardImg src={category.imgURL} alt={category.altText} />
                <CardTitle>{category.title}</CardTitle>
                <CardDescription>
                  {category.numberOfItems} items
                </CardDescription>
              </Fragment>
            ))}
            <CardImg
              src='https://image.flaticon.com/icons/svg/706/706195.svg'
              alt='Category Image'
            />
            <CardTitle>Food</CardTitle>
            <CardDescription>12 registers</CardDescription>
          </CardDiv>
          <CardDiv>
            <CardImg
              src='https://image.flaticon.com/icons/svg/1373/1373253.svg'
              alt='Category Image'
            />
            <CardTitle>House</CardTitle>
            <CardDescription>12 registers</CardDescription>
          </CardDiv>
          <CardDiv>
            <CardImg
              src='https://image.flaticon.com/icons/svg/706/706195.svg'
              alt='Category Image'
            />
            <CardTitle>Food</CardTitle>
            <CardDescription>12 registers</CardDescription>
          </CardDiv>
          <CardDiv>
            <CardImg
              src='https://image.flaticon.com/icons/svg/706/706195.svg'
              alt='Category Image'
            />
            <CardTitle>Food</CardTitle>
            <CardDescription>12 registers</CardDescription>
          </CardDiv>
          <CardDiv>
            <CardImg
              src='https://image.flaticon.com/icons/svg/706/706195.svg'
              alt='Category Image'
            />
            <CardTitle>Food</CardTitle>
            <CardDescription>12 registers</CardDescription>
          </CardDiv>
          <CardDiv>
            <CardImg
              src='https://image.flaticon.com/icons/svg/706/706195.svg'
              alt='Category Image'
            />
            <CardTitle>Food</CardTitle>
            <CardDescription>12 registers</CardDescription>
          </CardDiv>
        </CardContainer>
      </StyledContainer>
    )
  }
}
